OL,3,CUS and Iran consider 45-day ceasefire
OL,4,Cdeal while still pursuing war
OL,6,FITV News in Iran: International Editor
OL,7,FEmma Murphy reports on Trump's threats
OL,8,Fand talks of a temporary ceasefire deal
OL,10,FEveryone is warning of hell whilst
OL,11,Fapparently considering peace and still
OL,12,Fpursuing war.
OL,14,FSix weeks after the United States and
OL,15,FIsrael began their military campaign
OL,16,Fagainst Iran, the efforts to bring it
OL,17,Fto a halt continue with another set of
OL,18,Fceasefire proposals now apparently in
OL,19,Fthe hands of US and Iranian teams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
