OL,3,CUS and Iran consider 45-day ceasefire
OL,4,Cdeal while still pursuing war
OL,6,FPakistan has spearheaded these talks
OL,7,Fand the framework they are thought to
OL,8,Fhave laid out proposes an immediate
OL,9,Fceasefire and the reopening of the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz, with two to three
OL,11,Fweeks to agree a more expansive deal.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThe deal, dubbed the "Islamabad
OL,19,FAccord," aims for in person talks in
OL,20,FIslamabad.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
