OL,3,CUS and Iran consider 45-day ceasefire
OL,4,Cdeal while still pursuing war
OL,6,FIt seems unlikely Iran will accept a
OL,7,Ftemporary ceasefire. Only a permanent
OL,8,Fone would be enough for them to start
OL,9,Fto release their hold on the Strait
OL,10,Fand the world economy.
OL,12,FThe emergence of the framework detail
OL,13,Fcomes after another night of bombing
OL,14,Fand just hours after President Trump
OL,15,Ftold Iran's leaders they would be
OL,16,F"living in Hell" without the reopening
OL,17,Fof the Strait of Hormuz.
