OL,3,CUS and Iran consider 45-day ceasefire
OL,4,Cdeal while still pursuing war
OL,6,F"Tuesday will be Power Plant Day, and
OL,7,FBridge Day, all wrapped up in one, in
OL,8,FIran," Trump wrote on Truth Social on
OL,9,FSunday.
OL,11,FAdding, "There will be nothing like
OL,12,Fit!!! Open the Fuckin' Strait, you
OL,13,Fcrazy bastards, or you'll be living in
OL,14,FHell - JUST WATCH! Praise be to Allah."
OL,16,FThe comments have only compounded
OL,17,Fdisgust here in Iran at threats to
OL,18,Ftake the country back "to the stone
OL,19,Fages".
