OL,3,CUS and Iran consider 45-day ceasefire
OL,4,Cdeal while still pursuing war
OL,6,FIran for its part is also warning of
OL,7,Fopening the gates of hell if the
OL,8,Fcountry's energy infrastructure is hit.
OL,10,FMilitary commander Major General Ali
OL,11,FAbdollahi said: "We will target
OL,12,Fwithout restriction all infrastructure
OL,13,Fused by the terrorist US military, as
OL,14,Fwell as the infrastructure of the
OL,15,FZionist regime, with devastating and
OL,16,Fcontinuous strikes."
OL,18,FThat comment puts on alert the Gulf
OL,19,Fnations already feeling Iran's
OL,20,Fresponse over the past six weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
